Terrorists are very likely to try to carry out attacks in the Maldives. Attacks could be indiscriminate, including in places frequented by expatriates and foreign travellers including tourists.
In November 2017, the Maldivian authorities confirmed that a number of men had been arrested on terrorism charges.
